{"tid":847331,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"人生既意義，我已經參透到","createTime":"2018-10-04T05:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T15:59:06.000Z","uid":123335,"like":60,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8e081ca876b0fcec23e7c4873050b6c6c3dd0156","tid":847331,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:45:38.000Z","msg":"好簡單<br />\n兩隻字<br />\n「開心」<br />\n<br />\n而點為之「開心」？<br />\n人人唔同 <br />\n<br />\n有人會因為短暫既快樂而「開心」<br />\nEg 周圍flirt 女, 情場浪子, 賭博, 搵快錢, 奢華大洗 ...etc <br />\n<br />\n有人會因為達成長期目標而「開心」<br />\nEg 慢慢跳point 升職, 穩定關係, 有運動習慣keep fit ...etc <br />\n<br />\n有人亦會追求 why not both 而「開心」<br />\n既有短期快樂 又有長期目標 <br />\n<br />\n最緊要係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&rdquo;你覺得&rdquo;</span>開心<br />\n係一種你<span style=\"color: red;\">內在</span>既渴望與滿足<br />\n<br />\n點解係<span style=\"color: red;\">內在</span>？<br />\n舉個例, <br />\n有人會重視 身邊人既睇法<br />\n會想滿足身邊人既期望, 看似非常受外在因素影響<br />\nEg 為滿足父母期望, 而努力讀書 <br />\n但其實講白d , <br />\n呢個都<span style=\"color: red;\">係內在既慾望</span><br />\n你既<span style=\"color: red;\">內在</span>可以選擇重視父母既期望,<br />\n亦可以選擇忽視父母既期望而追求其他目標而快樂<br />\n<br />\n講到尾<br />\n人生既意義<br />\n好簡單<br />\n就係「<span style=\"color: red;\">你覺得</span>開心」就得"},{"pid":"75158a2f317d110818614e5111318306eca53f33","tid":847331,"uid":123335,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:50:48.000Z","msg":"認真post 冇人理 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6a24019f81dff9307d3f35bee66b6f37e70eaa","tid":847331,"uid":123335,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:53:10.000Z","msg":"出膠post 就咁多人覆<br />\n出認真post 就單機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cf57c2ec7a44a50317b95349495e2541e9605b","tid":847331,"uid":101945,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:54:55.000Z","msg":"你出post自己開心就好了"},{"pid":"2c3451f93f7268ddb2386c78c32a03ecbcca3b88","tid":847331,"uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{